  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paper Kingdom is a colony management game. Starting as a nomadic tribe your job is to turn your settlement into an empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Gather resources from cards like Forest, Quarry, Mine and Sea. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Craft items and assign jobs for your settlers. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Build structures to progress your settlement. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Produce goods and trade them for Coins.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore new cards and fight off invaders. </p></li></ul>",
